title: Worst Date Wednesday: He Wore a Shirt from The Buckle
description: Besty met a guy on a dating app and they decided to meet up to bowl but when they got to the bowling alley he didn't want to actually bowl because he "didn't want to pay to bowl on the 1st date".  WHAT?? Click to find out what happened on the rest of this awful date!
